{"categories":["others","computer-internet","business-services","transactional","marketing-and-design","media-entertainment"],"collections":"survey-campaign","description":"Immerse your audience in a digital experience with this dynamic email template, perfect for software and technology businesses, media and entertainment industries, and marketing and design services. With a vibrant blend of blue and orange hues, it's designed to capture attention and evoke a light, positive mood. The template features illustrative elements along with modern sans serif typography, subtly echoing the technology theme. Use this to send a confirmation of a successful survey or questionnaire completion, engaging your audience with interactive emojis and a thumbs-up sign. It's an effective tool to express gratitude for their opinion and participation, reinforcing your brand's commitment to customer satisfaction. This template is also versatile enough for other transactional business services, making it a must-have in your digital communication toolkit.","short_description":"Engage and thank your audience with this vibrant email template, perfect for technology businesses and media industries. Features include a dynamic blend of blue and orange hues, modern sans serif typography, and interactive emojis. Ideal for confirming survey completion and expressing gratitude.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/matteo-della-chiesa.jpg","description":"I've started to use Photoshop when I was 13. From 2009 to 2014, I've been a part of 5 Art Groups, doing Illustrations and Photo-manipulations, collaborating with over 150 Artists from all the Planet. In 2014, during my final school's exams, I've got my first Freelance Job at a Milan based Agency. Thanks to that first project, I started my Career as a Freelance Independent UI & Web Designer. Today, I help brands improve their online and digital presence, building usable, unique & beautiful products, mostly collab